import styled from 'styled-components'
import StyledCard from "../GenericStyledComponents/StyledCard";

const DoctorIntervalCardStyled = styled(StyledCard)``

const CardContent = styled.div`
    width: 25%;
`

const Date = styled(CardContent)``

const Day = styled(CardContent)``

const From = styled(CardContent)``

const To = styled(CardContent)``


export default { DoctorIntervalCardStyled, Date, Day, From, To }
